    "Then we measure the similarity of the node texts with BERTScore for successfully aligned nodes and compute micro averaged F1 score as following TP, FP, FN:",
    "where δ vr,v h = 1 iff v r and v h is aligned, and otherwise 0.",
    "For legal relations & transactions (edges), we extract the aligned edge label texts and compute F1 score from the similarity of labels.",
